{"tid":1398041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋人啟事］我有班兄弟自從7月26之後就失蹤 我想知道佢地現況","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:37:19.000Z","uid":159507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3fca8c8271f020c54fda127eed34cdd3b387fcf8","tid":1398041,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"七月尾你地一齊聯署既車長去咗邊呀<br />\n見你地咁多日都冇消息 我地香港人好擔心你地呀<br />\n香港人依家好需要你地支持 希望你地可以一齊踏出第一步<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8&middot;5 一齊全民大罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n我相信你地好多人都想罷工 但係怕比狗鐵秋後算帳 只要你地好似支持聯署咁集合晒大部分既力量 我好相信狗鐵係唔會秋後算帳你地架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人就係差你地既支持</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地既一小步 就係香港人既一大步</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地冇得再輸架啦<br />\n一輸成個香港就冇架啦</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>你哋有聯署既勇敢 希望你哋亦都有罷工既勇敢 </strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>更何況狗鐵高層好似林奠咁對於你地既訴求一啲都冇回應過</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/03/000146_c4ed56f11cd58dd6223f69208472d1cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F000146_c4ed56f11cd58dd6223f69208472d1cc.png&h=6683af5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/03/000147_9ec1bd1f91bfa3be1f690023ec230da7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F000147_9ec1bd1f91bfa3be1f690023ec230da7.png&h=44f8005a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/03/000150_c089a12afe5ac077798e8e2d8426d110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F000150_c089a12afe5ac077798e8e2d8426d110.png&h=a4710698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/03/000151_365e7eea4c949bd477a90ca0a6d2dc82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2F000151_365e7eea4c949bd477a90ca0a6d2dc82.png&h=8dfaba9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9f0cd0467ade311a35fdb9b944f11a1b3c59bc4","tid":1398041,"uid":34084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"414c88dacd58c657d5329a2da1f4fbdb9303430b","tid":1398041,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"推呀推到比車長見到"}]}